<lb n="1"/>koḷḷippākkaiyuḷ
<lb n="2"/>porutaṭariḻattaracar tamuṭi
<lb n="3"/>ṉṉavar pakkaṟ ṟeṉṉavaṉ
<lb n="4"/>Īḻamaṇṭala muḻuvatu meṟi
<lb n="5"/>palar pukaḻmuṭiyuñ ceṅkatir
<lb n="6"/>vaṟ palapaḻantivuñ ceruviṟ
<lb n="7"/>mevaruñ cāntimaṟṟivaraṇ karu<note n="439-1">Incomplete.</note>
</p>

